<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Payment Failed - Action Required</title>
    <style>
        body { margin: 0; padding: 0; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f5f5f5; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: #ffffff; }
        .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff6b6b 0%, #ee5a6f 100%); padding: 40px 20px; text-align: center; }
        .header h1 { color: #ffffff; margin: 0; font-size: 28px; }
        .content { padding: 40px 30px; }
        .content h2 { color: #333333; font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .content p { color: #666666; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 16px; }
        .cta-button { display: inline-block; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; padding: 15px 40px; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 600; margin: 20px 0; }
        .alert-box { background-color: #ffebee; border-left: 4px solid #d32f2f; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 8px; }
        .info-box { background-color: #f8f9fa; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 8px; }
        .footer { background-color: #f8f9fa; padding: 30px; text-align: center; color: #999999; font-size: 14px; }
        .footer a { color: #667eea; text-decoration: none; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Payment Failed</h1>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Hi <%= name %>,</h2>
            
            <div class="alert-box">
                <strong style="color: #c62828; font-size: 18px;">Action Required</strong>
                <p style="margin: 10px 0 0 0; color: #c62828;">We were unable to process your recent payment. Your account may be interrupted if this issue isn't resolved.</p>
            </div>
            
            <p>We attempted to charge your payment method, but the transaction failed. This could be due to:</p>
            
            <ul style="color: #666666; line-height: 1.8;">
                <li>Insufficient funds</li>
                <li>Expired credit/debit card</li>
                <li>Card declined by your bank</li>
                <li>Incorrect billing information</li>
            </ul>
            
            <div class="info-box">
                <strong style="color: #333;">ðŸ“‹ Payment Details:</strong>
                <ul style="color: #666; line-height: 1.8; margin: 10px 0 0 0;">
                    <li><strong>Amount:</strong> <%= amount || 'See billing page' %></li>
                    <li><strong>Billing Period:</strong> <%= billingPeriod || 'Monthly' %></li>
                    <li><strong>Next Retry:</strong> <%= retryDate || 'In 3 days' %></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <p><strong>To keep your account active:</strong></p>
            <ol style="color: #666666; line-height: 1.8;">
                <li>Update your payment method</li>
                <li>Ensure sufficient funds</li>
                <li>Contact your bank if needed</li>
                <li>Retry the payment manually</li>
            </ol>
            
            <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
                <a href="<%=  %>/dashboard/billing" class="cta-button">
                    Update Payment Method â†’
                </a>
            </div>
            
            <div style="background-color: #fff3e0; border-left: 4px solid #ff9800; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 30px 0;">
                <strong style="color: #e65100;">Important:</strong>
                <p style="margin: 10px 0 0 0; color: #e65100;">If payment isn't received within 7 days, your account will be downgraded to the free plan and you'll lose access to premium features.</p>
            </div>
            
            <p><strong>Need help?</strong> Our support team is here for you:</p>
            <ul style="color: #666666; line-height: 1.8;">
                <li>Reply to this email</li>
                <li>Visit our help center</li>
                <li>Contact billing support</li>
            </ul>
            
            <p>We understand payment issues happen. We're here to help you resolve this quickly!</p>
            
            <p style="margin-top: 30px;">Thank you for your attention,<br><strong>The Engagematic Team</strong></p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; <%= currentYear %> Engagematic. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>
                <a href="<%= preferencesUrl %>">Email Preferences</a> | 
                <a href="<%= unsubscribeUrl %>">Unsubscribe</a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>

